name: RabbitMQ for Beginners
body:
### Welcome to RabbitMQ for Beginners Pages.
This page is created for a presentation of [Wierd Developer Meetup in Melbourne](http://www.meetup.com/Weird-Developers-Melbourne/events/231588280) as a lightining talk.

You could find [the slide](https://github.com/AlexSangJoonPark/rabbitmq) and [example codes on GitHub](https://github.com/AlexSangJoonPark/rabbitmq)
